OL,3,CMum and daughter died following
OL,4,Ccollision on Plymouth pedestrian
OL,5,Ccrossing
OL,7,FA mother and daughter were killed when
OL,8,Fthey were in collision with a car as
OL,9,Fthey used a pedestrian crossing in
OL,10,FPlymouth, an inquest has heard.
OL,12,FDestiny Harrison, 24, and five-year-
OL,13,Fold Linnea Harrison died as they
OL,14,Fwalked across Victoria Road in 2024.
OL,16,FDevon Coroner's Court in Exeter heard
OL,17,FMs Harrison and her daughter were in
OL,18,Fcollision with a Nissan Qashqai car
OL,19,Fdriven by 76-year-old Brenda Marriott.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
