FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782893891
OL,3,CMum and daughter died following
OL,4,Ccollision on Plymouth pedestrian
OL,5,Ccrossing
OL,7,FEmergency services were called at
OL,8,Faround 9.45am on March 24 to a report
OL,9,Fof an accident involving the car and
OL,10,Ftwo pedestrians.
OL,12,FLinnea was pronounced dead at the
OL,13,Fscene while her mother died later at
OL,14,FDerriford Hospital, the inquest heard.
OL,16,FPathologist Dr Russell Delaney carried
OL,17,Fout post-mortem examinations and said
OL,18,FMs Harrison had suffered multiple
OL,19,Finjuries while her daughter had died
OL,20,Ffrom a head injury.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
