OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782893891
OL,3,CMum and daughter died following
OL,4,Ccollision on Plymouth pedestrian
OL,5,Ccrossing
OL,7,FIn a written statement, Mrs Marriott,
OL,8,Fwho did not attend the hearing, said
OL,9,Fshe was driving along Victoria Road
OL,10,Fwith a white car in front of her as
OL,11,Fshe approached the crossing.
OL,13,F"The white car went through it, it was
OL,14,Fstill green and I was following. I was
OL,15,Fdriving at 30mph," she said.
OL,17,F"I saw two shadows of pedestrians. The
OL,18,Fcar in front was higher than mine, so
OL,19,FI did not have a clear view.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@RO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
