OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782893891
OL,3,CMum and daughter died following
OL,4,Ccollision on Plymouth pedestrian
OL,5,Ccrossing
OL,7,F"When I drove closer, I saw the woman
OL,8,Fand a smaller person, with their heads
OL,9,Fdown, step out into the road.
OL,11,F"They were holding hands. They stepped
OL,12,Fout in front of my car."
OL,14,FMrs Marriott said she immediately
OL,15,Fbraked and came to a stop.
OL,17,F"I do believe the lights were green
OL,18,Fwhen I drove through and think that
OL,19,Fthe pedestrian misjudged the lights. I
OL,20,Fam so sorry, I am in shock," she added.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUtD@XO]yD@AOU|D@\O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
