CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782893891
OL,3,CMum and daughter died following
OL,4,Ccollision on Plymouth pedestrian
OL,5,Ccrossing
OL,7,FEyewitness Philip Askew was walking
OL,8,Fhis dog when he saw a woman and child
OL,9,Fheading towards the pedestrian
OL,10,Fcrossing but briefly turned away prior
OL,11,Fto the crash.
OL,13,F"I heard an almighty bang and then
OL,14,Fscream. I turned round immediately to
OL,15,Fsee what it was," he said.
OL,17,FMr Askew said others went immediately
OL,18,Fto give first aid to Ms Harrison and
OL,19,Fher daughter.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
