PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782893891
OL,3,CMum and daughter died following
OL,4,Ccollision on Plymouth pedestrian
OL,5,Ccrossing
OL,7,FHe added: "I did not see a pedestrian
OL,8,Fstep out into the road.
OL,10,F"I did not see the colour of the
OL,11,Fpedestrian control traffic lights at
OL,12,Fthe time and collision itself. I did
OL,13,Fnot see the collision itself take
OL,14,Fplace."
OL,16,FKaren Bull, who lives nearby, said she
OL,17,Fheard a noise that sounded like a car
OL,18,Fover-revving.
OL,20,F"I didn't see the car, I just heard
OL,21,Fit," she said.
OL,26,@oD@KOUrD@AOUvD@GO]|D@AOU}D@DO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
