OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782893891
OL,3,CMum and daughter died following
OL,4,Ccollision on Plymouth pedestrian
OL,5,Ccrossing
OL,7,F"The pedestrians were crossing the
OL,8,Froad. My attention was drawn to the
OL,9,Fpedestrians, so I didn't look to see
OL,10,Fthe colour of the lights on the
OL,11,Fcrossing.
OL,13,F"They appeared to be walking calmly
OL,14,Fand at normal pace. I heard a horrible
OL,15,Fnoise. I can't get the noise out of my
OL,16,Fhead."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
