PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782893891
OL,3,CMum and daughter died following
OL,4,Ccollision on Plymouth pedestrian
OL,5,Ccrossing
OL,7,FPc Mel Inness, a forensic collision
OL,8,Finvestigator, said there were no
OL,9,Fdefects with the car and there was no
OL,10,Fevidence from the scene to assist with
OL,11,Fassessing speed or reaction time of
OL,12,Fthe driver.
OL,14,FShe said: "There was nothing within
OL,15,Fthe physical evidence to indicate
OL,16,Femergency braking immediately prior to
OL,17,For post-impact but this does not
OL,18,Fpreclude it from having occurred.
OL,26,@vD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
