OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782893891
OL,3,CMum and daughter died following
OL,4,Ccollision on Plymouth pedestrian
OL,5,Ccrossing
OL,7,F"It is not known what colour the
OL,8,Ftraffic lights were at the point the
OL,9,FNissan approached the collision scene
OL,10,For at what point the pedestrians
OL,11,Fstepped in the road.
OL,13,F"There is nothing from within the
OL,14,Fphysical evidence from which I can
OL,15,Fcalculate speed at impact, or on the
OL,16,Fapproach to."
OL,18,FThe inquest continues.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUxD@MO]
